text: Cullendale is an unincorporated community in Ouachita County, Arkansas, United States. It is part of the Camden Micropolitan Statistical Area and lies at an elevation of 128 ft. ==References== ==External links== *Cullendale (Arkansas, United States - USA) *Cullendale, Arkansas (AR) *http://ouachitacountyhistoricalsociety.org/Cullendale2.pdf Category:Unincorporated communities in Arkansas Category:Unincorporated communities in Ouachita County, Arkansas Category:Camden, Arkansas micropolitan area
